436
00:31:48,359 --> 00:31:51,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu harus mencoba pakaian. Cepat!</font>

437
00:31:56,740 --> 00:31:58,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini? Aku akan mencoba pakaianku di sini?</font>

438
00:31:58,970 --> 00:32:02,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus mengetes kehangatannya.</font>

439
00:32:02,270 --> 00:32:04,909
