445
00:32:20,290 --> 00:32:23,099
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kita pergi, mari berfoto. Berfotolah denganku.</font>

446
00:32:23,099 --> 00:32:24,899
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini luar biasa. Aku menyukainya.</font>

447
00:32:24,899 --> 00:32:27,530
