448
00:32:28,470 --> 00:32:31,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kamu membawaku ke sini malam-malam begini?</font>

449
00:32:31,369 --> 00:32:33,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang terpenting, kenapa aku di sini bersamamu?</font>

